    "Finally, Fig. 14 shows the normalized energy in comparison to Atleus showing increased gains upon quantization for transformer models GPT-2 (Medium) and BLOOM-560m.",
    "It is evident that Atleus' energy reduces as the quantization level increases.",
    "In contrast, HAIMA, 3D-TPU, and GPU demonstrate an increase in energy consumption under similar conditions.",
    "This differential behavior underscores the efficiency of the Atleus architecture enabled by crossbar-wise quantization.",
